---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Cookie Policy · DittoFS"
  description="The cookies the DittoFS website uses and how to control them."
>
  <article class="legal mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20">
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      We keep cookies to a minimum. Nothing beyond what is strictly necessary
      loads until you opt in.
    </p>

    <h2>Categories</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Necessary.</strong> Required for the site to function and to
        remember your cookie choices. Always on.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Analytics.</strong> Google Tag Manager and the tags it loads,
        used to measure traffic and usage. Loaded only with your consent.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Marketing.</strong> The Meta (Facebook) pixel, used to measure
        and improve our advertising. Loaded only with your consent.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Managing your choices</h2>
    <p>
      You can change or withdraw your consent at any time.
    </p>
    <p>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="btn btn-secondary"
        onclick="window.openCookiePreferences && window.openCookiePreferences()"
      >
        Manage cookie preferences
      </button>
    </p>
    <p>
      You can also clear cookies in your browser settings, which will prompt the
      consent banner again on your next visit.
    </p>

    <h2>More information</h2>
    <p>
      See our <a href="/privacy/">privacy policy</a> for how we handle the data
      these cookies collect.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
